::KitKat::
She came running into the battle at full speed.  She leaded up and 
transformed into bot mode.  She saw Megatron standing there(not 
knowing it was the clone) and looked at him. "Megatron, You left us 
to die. Now it's your turn."  She drew her rifle and gun up and aimed 
them at Megatron. 

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, JP3884@a... wrote:
>     Inferno, and two of the clones converged on Starscream 
> like...well....ants. Inferno fell to the ground with the fire, but 
two of the 
> clones sent a solid stream of fire each at Star Scream, and when 
Inferno got 
> himself together, pelted him with several fire balls.
>     
>     The clone of Megatron arrived on the scene. He looked at the 
battle, and 
> in his zombie like state raised his pistol and let off a few blasts 
at the 
> oncoming Kitkat. That was the main target, her or Phobia.
